flowchart TD
    A[User Registers Account] --> B[User Logs In]
    B --> C[User Browses Events]
    C --> D[User Selects Event]
    D --> E[User Fills Registration Form]
    E --> F{User Agrees to Terms?}
    F -->|No| E
    F -->|Yes| G[Create Consent Log]
    G --> H[Submit Registration]
    H --> I[Registration Status: Pending]
    I --> J[Admin Reviews Registration]
    J --> K{Admin Decision}
    K -->|Approve| L[Status: Approved]
    K -->|Reject| M[Status: Rejected]
    L --> N[User Receives Notification]
    M --> N
    N --> O[User Can View Status]
    O --> P{User Requests GDPR Action?}
    P -->|Export Data| Q[Create DataRequest: Export]
    P -->|Correct Data| R[Create DataRequest: Correction]
    P -->|Delete Account| S[Create DataRequest: Deletion]
    Q --> T[Admin Processes Request]
    R --> T
    S --> T
    T --> U[Request Status: Completed]
    U --> V[End]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style I fill:#fff3cd
    style L fill:#d4edda
    style M fill:#f8d7da
    style T fill:#d1ecf1
    style V fill:#e1f5ff

